about.summary: Similarly to Schafer's package 'pan', 'jomo' is a package for multilevel joint modelling multiple imputation (Carpenter and Kenward, 2013) <doi: 10.1002/9781119942283>. Novel aspects of 'jomo' are the possibility of handling binary and categorical data through latent normal variables, the option to use cluster-specific covariance matrices and to impute compatibly with the substantive model.

name: r-jomo
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.7-0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-jomo
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/jomo_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/jomo/jomo_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ef4c27b7a8432777d863ffb281ebd2b848b88099832d8167ed43b9a1b9a8b6eb

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-lme4
    - r-ordinal
    - r-survival
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-mass
    - r-lme4
    - r-ordinal
    - r-survival

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('jomo')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('jomo')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=jomo
  license: GPL-2
  summary: "Similarly to Schafer's package 'pan', 'jomo' is a package for multilevel joint modelling multiple imputation (Carpenter and Kenward, 2013) <doi: 10.1002/9781119942283>. Novel aspects of 'jomo' are the possibility of handling binary and categorical data through latent normal variables, the option to use cluster-specific\
    \ covariance matrices and to impute compatibly with the substantive model. "
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
